{"per_page":10,"total":16,"current":12,"data":[{"title":"jQuery 属性操作 - attr() 方法","date":"2018-07-25T02:13:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>项目代码,需要点击图片后，弹出dailog窗口，显示完整图片</p>\n<p>html部分<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;div class=&quot; user_upload_images&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;img src=&quot;&#123;php echo tomedia($item[&apos;content_image&apos;])&#125;&quot; class=&quot;imgg&quot; style=&quot;width:40px;height:40px;padding:1px;border:1px solid #ccc;&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">//dialog提示框</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;div id=&quot;dialog&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;img src=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;show_big_image&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">//使用jqueryUi</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;//apps.bdimg.com/libs/jqueryui/1.10.4/css/jquery-ui.min.css&quot;&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script src=&quot;//apps.bdimg.com/libs/jquery/1.10.2/jquery.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;script src=&quot;//apps.bdimg.com/libs/jqueryui/1.10.4/jquery-ui.min.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>js部分<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$(function () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       $(&quot;#dialog&quot;).dialog(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           autoOpen: false,</span><br><span class=\"line\">           show: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         </span><br><span class=\"line\">           &#125;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">           hide: &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           </span><br><span class=\"line\">           &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">       $(&quot;.imgg&quot;).click(function () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           $(&quot;#dialog&quot;).dialog(&quot;open&quot;);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t//当点击 class=imgg 的标签时，将id=show_big_image标签中的src属性赋值成 class=imgg 的标签中的src属性的值</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t$(&quot;#show_big_image&quot;).attr(&quot;src&quot;,$(this).attr(&quot;src&quot;));</span><br><span class=\"line\">       &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/164","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"mybatis中的事务管理器 TransactionManager基础知识","date":"2018-07-23T05:55:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>transactionManager提供了两个实现类，但是这两个实现类必须实现Transaction这个接口<br>Transaction中包含了三个重要的方法：commit（提交）、rollback（回滚），close（关闭）<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">public interfance Transaction&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   Connection getConnection() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  void commit() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  void rollback() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  void close() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  Integer getTimeout() throws SQLException;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/159","categories":["Mybatis"]},{"title":"php中判断一个时间是今天的时间","date":"2018-07-23T01:57:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/158","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"git 添加文件未识别","date":"2018-07-16T23:07:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/157","categories":["Git"]},{"title":"redis安装","date":"2018-07-13T19:51:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>####进入系统软件目录<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cd /usr/local/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<h4 id=\"解压\">解压<a href=\"post/153#解压\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">tar -zxvf redis-3.0.0-rc2.tar.gz -C /usr/local/</span><br><span class=\"line\">cd ./redis-3.0.0-rc2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h4 id=\"编译\">编译<a href=\"post/153#编译\"></a></h4><p><strong>进行编译 ，前提是需要有gcc库</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">make   </span><br><span class=\"line\">//出现Hint: It&apos;s a good idea to run &apos;make test&apos; ;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">说明编译成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<h4 id=\"安装redis\">安装redis<a href=\"post/153#安装redis\"></a></h4><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> cd ./src/</span><br><span class=\"line\">make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<p>安装完成<br><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/3304785728.png\" alt><br></p>","link":"post/153","categories":["Redis"]},{"title":"Orcale存储过程事物","date":"2018-07-11T22:37:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/145","categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"Orcale存储过程demo和走的坑","date":"2018-07-10T22:37:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>orcale的坑<br><strong>1、定义的存储过程的名一定要和最后END的时候的名字一样</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">create or replace procedure &quot;Pro_Sprk_Cancel&quot;(</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br><span class=\"line\">as</span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br><span class=\"line\">begin</span><br><span class=\"line\">end &quot;Pro_Sprk_Cancel&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p><strong>2、存储过程中用的一切参数一定要定义</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">create or replace procedure &quot;Pro_Sprk_Cancel&quot;(</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br><span class=\"line\">as</span><br><span class=\"line\"> --定义变量</span><br><span class=\"line\"> num number;</span><br><span class=\"line\">drug_num number;</span><br><span class=\"line\">begin</span><br><span class=\"line\">  begin</span><br><span class=\"line\">     select count(1) into drug_num from &quot;his_system_drug_info&quot; ;     </span><br><span class=\"line\">     select count(1) into num from &quot;his_pharmacy_storage&quot; ;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     end;    </span><br><span class=\"line\">end &quot;Pro_Sprk_Cancel&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/137","categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"plsql 永久注册码适用各个版本","date":"2018-07-09T22:11:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/136","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"php 小数整理,向上取整,向下去整,四舍五入,丢弃小数部分,保留整数部分","date":"2018-07-05T23:23:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/135","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"微信小程序获得服务器ip","date":"2018-07-03T02:53:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>错误：<br>    有时候在小程序前端能取到图片的地址，但是不显示<br>解决方法：<br>    可能是数据库中只存了图片的服务器地址，但是地址不全<br>    例：<br>    <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/pages/member/info/index</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>但如果要显示到页面上需要加ip。即：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">192.168.100.103/pages/member/info/index</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/134","categories":["Other"]}]}